Exceptional Sans Souci Cruise in Halong Bay
This was an outstanding trip for 2 days 1 night provided by Mr Hao and his crew through Halong Bay. My boyfriend and I were part of a mixed group of 9 people and we had a superb time. The boat itself was very clean and well presented. We were both shocked at how big our double bedroom and ensuite bathroom was, which included a great rainforest shower cubicle. As soon as we boarded the boat the staff were extremely friendly and helpful and catered for our needs throughout the trip very well. They also were really keen to participate in Kareoke during the evening, which made it less painless for the embarassed tourists. But everyone was really keen to get involved and soon there was no stopping us! The places we visited were amazing too. The caves, fishing village and swimming lagoon were thoroughly enjoyable, which was matched perfectly with your own free time on deck to soak up the atmosphere of the beautiful bay and rock formations. Sunset was very special too. The food served on board was exceptional. From the moment we stepped foot on board we were provided with the most delicious selection of seafood imaginable. We defintiely didn't go hungry at any point and we were so impressed with the food quality it's difficult to explain without eating it for yourself. We did the 2 day 1 night trip due to the weather conditions but if we could have we would have loved to have stayed on the boat for another day. I thoroughly reccommend this tour to anybody as we met some fantastic people - it wasn't just couple oriented or people of certain ages - a real mix! Well worth the money spent, it has left us with some fantastic memories. Thank you Sans Souci Cruise!
